item.title: quick note about NFT
item.description: it has come to our attention that a number of users aren’t happy that we minted their arts as NFTs. well, some of these NFTs are now making money and we’d like the opportunity to make it right. if you have an irc art archived on this website, you could be eligible for compensation. in order to check if we have any funds to disburse to you, please enter your main irc alias in the form below and verify the captcha to submit.
